  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Sustainable, Child Labor Free Vanilla-Growing Communities in Sava</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project &#x201C;Supporting Sustainable, Child Labor Free Vanilla-Growing Communities in Sava&#x201D; expresses the vision of the International Labor Organization (ILO), the Sustainable Vanilla Initiative (SVI) and their national and international partners for a transformed vanilla sector in Madagascar. The project&#x2019;s goal is to significantly reduce the prevalence of child labor in Sava and more than that, to contribute to vanilla becoming a source of prosperity for vanilla-growing communities through fair and sustainable livelihoods for small-holder vanilla farmers and their families and decent work for adults and youth of legal working age.</narrative>
  </description>
